Standard Chartered Bank Ghana to Pay Preference-Share Dividend

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-09-28T09:02:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/standard-chartered-bank-ghana-to-pay-preference-share-dividend.html
Standard Chartered Bank Ghana Ltd.
will pay a dividend of 0.0404 cedi for each preference share on
Sept. 30 for the year through December, the company said in a
statement published in the Accra-based Ghanaian Times today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Moses Mozart Dzawu in Accra at 
 mdzawu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  